# Gemini CLI Ignore File
# 屏蔽对 AI 抓取上下文无用或噪音过大的目录和文件，节省 Token 并提高搜索精度

# 早期废弃或发散性的草稿
草稿/

# Unity 引擎生成的冗余文件与目录
*.meta
UnityClient/Packages/
UnityClient/Library/
UnityClient/Temp/
UnityClient/Obj/
UnityClient/Build/
UnityClient/Builds/
UnityClient/UserSettings/
UnityClient/MemoryCaptures/
UnityClient/Recordings/

# 日志文件体积庞大，仅在排查 Bug 时精准定向读取，全局搜索时必须排除
UnityClient/Logs/
*.log

# C# 编译与工程文件
*.csproj
*.sln
*.suo
*.tmp
*.user
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
*.pdb
*.mdb
*.opendb
*.VC.db

# 视觉资产 (AI 无法通过文本有效分析的内容)
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.tga
*.psd
*.fbx
*.obj
*.mat
*.anim
*.controller
*.wav
*.mp3
*.ogg

# OS 自动生成文件
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
